While living together, it is possible to see the daily activities of children together and find a solution to the problem together. But if you separate and the children live with one of you, there is bound to be trouble."

Children also use this opportunity to start the field of character degradation. Then they fall into bad habits and behavior. They will be a problem for the poor and not good for themselves or the country. You have to be very careful, especially on your part, so that children don't end up with such a terrible life.
